{
  "day": "1",
  "heading": "Drive from Manali to Dhundi via Palchan. Trek from Dhundi to Palchhani Thatch",
  "sub_heading": "Drive Distance: 14 km | Drive Duration: 1.5 hours | Trek Distance: 1.5 km | Trek Duration: 1 hour\nAltitude Gain: 9,317 ft to 10,134 ft",
  "details": "Leave from Beas Bridge, Manali, Manali at 8.30 am. Ensure you have had your breakfast before reaching the pickup point. En route, drop off your cloakroom bag, collect your rentals, and offload if you have opted for it, at Palchan. You will meet your trek leader here.\nIndiahikes will arrange transport for the transfer from Manali to Dhundi. This pickup costs ₹900 (additional 5% GST) per trekker one way from Manali to Dhundi (₹1800 for onward and return journeys). These are non-AC vehicles. Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek.\nYou start the trek at Dhundi. From Dhundi, you will reach your first campsite at Palchhani Thatch by 2.30 pm and have lunch there."
}

