{
  "day": "4",
  "heading": "Lohali to Dhundi. Drive back to Manali",
  "sub_heading": "Trek distance: 4 km | Trek Duration: 4 hours\nAltitude loss: 11050 ft to 9,317 ft |  Drive back cost: Rs 3,600 per vehicle to be shared by trekkers",
  "details": "Indiahikes will arrange transport from Dhundi to Beas Bridge, Manali. The cost for this drop-off is ₹800 (additional 5% GST) per trekker one way from Dhundi to Beas Bridge, Manali (₹1800 for onward and return journeys). These are non-AC vehicles. Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek.\nStop at Palchan to return rentals and collect your cloakroom luggage.\nYou will be back to Beas Bridge, Manali by 4 pm.\nPlease note: The distance between campsites may vary by 100 meters depending on the weather conditions and the route you take. The altitude may also vary by 100 feet for similar reasons."
}
